
HEXTETRIS
=========

Conversion of the Tetris available on MSX2 computer.

Requirement: 1 MB RAM

Installation: it requires an ASSIGN (for instance, ASSIGN HEXTETRIS: WORK:GAMES/HEXTETRIS)

Authors: Eugenio Favaro, Mirko benedettini


CONTROLS
--------

EFFECT                   KEYBOARD             JOYSTICK

Preview on/off           cursor key up        joy up
Move block to left       cursor key left      joy left
Move block down quickly  cursor keu down      joy down
Move block to right      cursor key right     joy right
Pause game               'escape key          -
Music on/off             'm' key              -
Trainer menu             'return' key         -

(Trainer menu only available while the game is paused)

